title: Cinch Men's Silver Label Dark Wash Mid Rise Slim Straight Performance Jeans Dark Stone 35W x 36L
description: Cinch Jeans are designed for your cowboy lifestyle - in and out of the saddle Cinch jeans are continually updating styles and washes, along with ensuring great fits, finishes, quality denim and an extraordinary attention to detail. So Cinch is proud to showcase their Silver Label Performance denim jeans. These men's Cinch jeans sport a convenient button waist with zipper fly. Authentic five-pocket construction. Men's Cinch jeans are made of 100% premium cotton denim. Imported.
